  "body": "Our controllers use a variety of different patterns for data-polling, none of which support simultaneous use of multiple networks. We should update all of them to use one consistent polling pattern that supports simultaneous use of multiple networks. \n\nThere may be additional patterns which need to be applied or help needed in order to support the ongoing multichain effort. ",
